Birla Corporation Ltdhas informed BSE that the meeting of the Board of Directors of the Company is scheduled on 09/05/2025 inter alia to consider and approve 1) the Standalone and Consolidated Audited Financial Results of the Company for the quarter and year ended 31st March 2025;
2) recommend dividend if any on the equity shares of the Company for the financial year ended 31st March 2025;
3) issuance of Non-Convertible Debentures on Private  Placement basis.
